Rules for confidence values:
- 0.0-0.3: Clearly legitimate (system emails, known contacts, normal correspondence)
- 0.3-0.5: Slightly suspicious but probably legitimate
- 0.5-0.7: Moderately suspicious, needs review
- 0.7-0.9: Likely spam/phishing with clear indicators
- 0.9-1.0: Obviously spam/phishing with multiple strong indicators